<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mustakhine | Portfolio</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset some default styles */
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Header Section */
        header {
            background-color: #24292e;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 80px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        header h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        header p {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #ddd;
        }

        /* Sections */
        section {
            padding: 60px 20px;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: auto;
        }

        section h2 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #24292e;
        }

        section p {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        /* Projects Cards */
        .projects {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
        }
        .project-card {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            width: 250px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }
        .project-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
        .project-card h3 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #0366d6;
        }
        .project-card p {
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        /* Button */
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #0366d6;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.2s;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #024c9a;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            background-color: #24292e;
            color: #fff;
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media(max-width: 600px) {
            header h1 { font-size: 36px; }
            section h2 { font-size: 28px; }
            .projects { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>Mustakhine</h1>
    <p>Welcome to my personal portfolio website</p>
</header>

<section>
    <h2>About Me</h2>
    <p>Hi! Iâ€™m Mustakhine, learning web development and building amazing projects. I love coding, experimenting with new technologies, and sharing what I learn.</p>
</section>

<section>
    <h2>My Projects</h2>
    <div class="projects">
        <div class="project-card">
            <h3>Project 1</h3>
            <p>A simple website built using HTML and CSS.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="project-card">
            <h3>Project 2</h3>
            <p>A GitHub Pages portfolio template for beginners.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="project-card">
            <h3>Project 3</h3>
            <p>Learning JavaScript and interactive web projects.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section>
    <h2>Contact Me</h2>
    <p>If you want to connect or see more projects, click the button below!</p>
    <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="mailto:youremail@example.com" class="btn">Contact Me</a>
    </div>
</section>

<footer>
    <p>&copy; 2026 Mustakhine | All rights reserved</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
